text: Polypedates pseudotilophus is a species of frogs in the family Rhacophoridae. It is endemic to Sumatra and Java in Indonesia. ==References== * Matsui, Hamidy & Kuraishi, 2014 : A new species of Polypedates from Sumatra, Indonesia (Amphibia: Anura). title: Polypedates pseudotilophus
